TROY SPEAR UNDERWATER ROBOTICS
ROBOSUB 2024 TECHNICAL DESIGN REPORT (TDR)

This PDF file is a placeholder for the 2024 Technical Design Report for the vehicle: Triton.

This document details the complete design, engineering, and testing phases of the Triton AUV, including:
1. SolidWorks hull stress analysis and rapid-prototyped composite thruster ducts.
2. Custom electronic speed controller (ESC) carrier board PCB layouts.
3. High-level path planning state machines (SMC) and OpenCV color segmentation.
4. Active pitch/roll PID tuning trials and depth-holding calibration graphs.
5. Torpedo pneumatic launcher launch trajectories and acoustic hydrophone arrays.

Competition Result: RoboSub 2024 Top 12, Best Technical Documentation Award Winner.
